---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- CBA Siege Data
-- Siege blueprint constants, per-civilization siege unit mappings, and lookup helpers
-- Consumed by: ags_no_dock.scar (NoSiege lock), cba.scar (siege limits), cba_options.scar
-- Split from ags_no_dock.scar for maintainability
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

